No established error range was found New Straits Time ethnic composition.There are disputed ethnic figures for DUN Serembu. Borneo Post (22/2/2016) figures are used for Serembu as New Straits Times data is errorneous in nature. Original Source Data for age group of 50 - 59 for DUN Tupong was an error and was corrected by Tindak Malaysia. Similarly, correction was made for the age group of 70 - 79 for DUN Bukit Goram as original data source had error.
